dct_description_sm: Bar scales on maps given in "Scale milia Italiani."
Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margins of L'Isola Cuba.
Enlarged versions of Jacopo Gastaldi's "Isola Spagnola nova" and "Isola Cuba nova" from Ptolemy, Geographia, Venice, 1548.
Re-engraved versions of maps with same titles by Paulo Forlani, Venice, 1564.
